inputs.prompt: An ultra-realistic, colossal seven-headed fire-breathing dragon standing atop a scorched volcanic mountain. Each head has a distinct personality and expression—rage, intelligence, hunger, dominance, cruelty, vigilance, and ancient wisdom. Molten lava drips between obsidian scales, glowing from within as if heat pulses beneath the skin. Massive wings spread wide, tattered and burned at the edges, casting an enormous shadow through thick smoke and ash. Multiple streams of fire erupt from its heads simultaneously, illuminating the dark storm-filled sky with explosive orange and crimson light. Hyper-detailed textures, realistic muscle anatomy, cinematic lighting, dramatic contrast, shallow depth of field, epic scale, 8K ultra-realism, dark fantasy atmosphere, awe-inspiring and terrifying.
